commit.message: Small improvements
clean up
Add information to the readme regarding the new output format.

Implemented the `start_time` in a different manner. As each worker will
 have their own process with their own object `ReplayPlugin` and it is
interesting to have the initial time equal for all those workers.
It is using the `pytest_cmdline_main` hook which will add as an
option the start time of the pytest. So, in that way all workers will
have the same initial time.

Implementation to pytest-replay to be backward compatible with the
current implementation. In that way it will be possible to execute
"old" output files.

Add tests to cover the possibility to execute the plugin using
the current format
Tests improvements and modified tests to be able to run the new output format
WIP
Modify test_normal_execution to run the new output format
